text: Stephanie Bukovec (born 22 September 1995) is a Croatian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Croatia women's national team. ==Career== Bukovec has been capped for the Croatia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian women's footballers Category:Croatia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Oakland Golden Grizzlies women's soccer players Category:Belmont Bruins women's soccer players Category:Canadian people of Croatian descent Category:Canadian women's soccer players Category:AFC Ajax (women) players Category:ŽNK Split players
